CatDescriptText: Musicians in the image are playing bongos, snare drums, saxophones and a trumpet.
TitMainTitle: Man holding money, and woman wearing flowered hat and evening gown, seated at table in front of Little Paris band, including Will Smith or Puggie on bongos, Joni Wilson on drums, Jim "Jimmy" Swan on trumpet, Alex Nelson on baritone saxophone, Charles "Chuck" Reeves on alto saxophone, and Roy Hamilton on piano, at Little Paris Club
